_aChangeLog.text: Added winner and losers box to deathrun
Can no longer cheat in jump rope
Jump rope and Wipeout enflict less damage
Less chance of Breakfloor game breaking every block
Added signs under labels so they are easier to read
Unpacked files not needed for smaller file size
Colours now works on walls as well as the ceiling
Added more masks around the map

_sText:
Designed and mapped by StyleZ.
==================

Notes
------------------
I found this great texture pack by Sethan and was inspired to make a new map. It has grown to be very popular map after a few beta versions.

Map features
------------------
- Vent system under most of the map
- Secret room
- Secret hole in a crate
- 1 of 2 vent cells per round

Activities
------------------
- Dodge the crate
- Deathrun
- Race (Changes every round)
- Colours (Simon Says)
- Breakfloor
- Dodgeball
- Climb
- Jump rope
- Wipeout
- Traitor

Credits
------------------
